<T>__{dissolve to:}
<L>__{interior hotel corridor. day.}
<A>__{paul knocks on a door. the tutsi politician xavier opens the door, sees that it is paul.}
<C>__{xavier}
<D>__{come in paul.}
<L>__{interior hotel luxury suite. day}
<A>__{a beautiful two bedroom suite. xavier lives in comfort compared to the other refugees.}
